Company Overview of Empyrean Capital Partners, LP



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Empyrean Capital Partners, LP is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm primarily provides its services to other pooled investment vehicles. It launches and manages hedge funds for its clients. The firm invests in public equity markets. It also invests in alternative investments markets. The firm invests in value stocks by employing event-driven strategy with fundamental analysis and bottom-up approach to make its investments. Empyrean Capital Partners, LP was founded in April 2004 and is based in Los Angeles, California.


